            <lg xml:id="TK1321">
<l>illai tavaṟavark kāyiṉum mūṭutal </l>
<l> valla tavaraḷikku māṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although my husband is free from defects, the way in which he embraces me is such as to make me feign dislike.</l>
